1
00:00:27,166 --> 00:00:30,875
ERA LA NOTTE PRIMA DI NATALE

2
00:00:34,708 --> 00:00:36,708
[musica fiabesca]

3
00:00:56,125 --> 00:00:57,791
[respiri profondi]

4
00:00:57,875 --> 00:00:59,458
[bambina] Billy, svegliati.

5
00:00:59,541 --> 00:01:00,541
Eh?

6
00:01:01,833 --> 00:01:02,833
Hai sentito?

7
00:01:06,041 --> 00:01:07,500
Sentito cosa?

8
00:01:07,583 --> 00:01:09,250
- [leggero tonfo]
- [sussulta]

9
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,875
È lui!

10
00:01:19,916 --> 00:01:21,916
[musica misteriosa]

11
00:01:23,416 --> 00:01:27,083
[bambino in TV] <i>Non ci posso credere!
Guarda, è Babbo Natale!</i>

12
00:01:27,166 --> 00:01:29,000
- Pss!
- [Babbo Natale in TV] <i>Eccomi.</i>

13
00:01:29,083 --> 00:01:31,083
[TV continua in sottofondo]

14
00:01:42,291 --> 00:01:46,916
[Babbo Natale in TV] ... <i>e ora consegnerò
tutti questi regali in un batter d'occhio.</i>

15
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,958
[bambino in TV] <i>È fantastico,
Babbo Natale! Ne ho un altro.</i>

16
00:01:51,625 --> 00:01:56,875
<i>Quindi andrai in giro tutta la notte
a consegnare regali in tutto il mondo?</i>

17
00:01:56,958 --> 00:01:58,583
[Babbo Natale in TV] <i>Sì, esatto.</i>

18
00:01:58,666 --> 00:02:02,041
[bambino in TV] <i>Spero di ricevere
la macchinina che volevo tanto.</i>

19
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:08,083
[leggero tramestio]

20
00:02:12,875 --> 00:02:14,250
[sussulta]

21
00:02:17,958 --> 00:02:19,125
[grugnito]

22
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:21,125
[rutto]

23
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:23,041
[mostro mastica]

24
00:02:26,583 --> 00:02:29,583
- [sussulta]
- [musica inquietante]

25
00:02:30,625 --> 00:02:32,458
[mostro ringhia]

26
00:02:36,708 --> 00:02:39,208
[musica in crescendo]

27
00:02:43,083 --> 00:02:44,083
[Billy sussulta]

28
00:02:44,166 --> 00:02:45,083
[mostro strilla]

29
00:02:45,166 --> 00:02:46,833
[urla]

30
00:02:48,875 --> 00:02:51,000
[musica inquietante culmina]

31
00:02:51,083 --> 00:02:51,916
[squittio]

32
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,250
[grida]

33
00:02:54,041 --> 00:02:56,750
- [ringhia]
- [ansima]

34
00:02:57,875 --> 00:02:59,625
[annusa]

35
00:03:03,041 --> 00:03:05,916
[ringhiando] Leah...

36
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,416
brava.

37
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,416
[piange]

38
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:12,625
[conati di vomito]

39
00:03:26,250 --> 00:03:28,166
[ringhiando] William...

40
00:03:29,166 --> 00:03:31,166
- [William geme]
- [annusa]

41
00:03:38,583 --> 00:03:40,333
...bravo.

42
00:03:40,416 --> 00:03:42,916
[rigurgito rumoroso]

43
00:03:47,666 --> 00:03:48,666
[sussulta]

44
00:03:53,916 --> 00:03:57,875
[mostro] Continua a fare il bravo.

45
00:03:57,958 --> 00:03:59,833
[ringhia]

46
00:04:00,458 --> 00:04:02,666
[passi in allontanamento]

47
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:04,750
[mostro ringhia]

48
00:04:09,208 --> 00:04:12,375
[ansimano]

49
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:20,500
[musica di suspense in crescendo]

50
00:04:23,208 --> 00:04:25,208
[musica sfuma]

51
00:04:28,875 --> 00:04:32,458
È... è proprio quello che volevo.

52
00:04:37,083 --> 00:04:37,958
Billy...

53
00:04:39,333 --> 00:04:44,458
che sarebbe accaduto
se non fossimo stati... bravi?

54
00:04:45,625 --> 00:04:47,625
[musica natalizia riprende]

55
00:04:53,291 --> 00:04:55,291
[mostro ruggisce]

56
00:04:56,250 --> 00:04:58,250
[musica sfuma]

